LocalMachine:-
  http://localhost:3000/restfulservices/v1/users/{id}
  http = protocol
  localhost = Host(domain name)
  3000 = Port
  restfulservices = Application context
  v1 = versioning
  users = Resource, like Products name
  {id} = parameter, like Query/Route param

ServerMachine:-
  https://amazon:3000/restfulservices/v1/users/1



Note:-Once again gothrought the Airtribe platform
      NodeJS-> Module 2-> Rest APIs - Best Practies.
